title: Tech draws Auburn for opening round of NCAAs - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech draws Auburn for opening round of NCAAs - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, TEXAS --Â  The Texas Tech Men's tennis team has punched its ticket to the NCAA tournament and will travel to Winton-Salem to face the Auburn Tigers in the Opening Round of the 2022 NCAA Tournament Friday. First serve from North Carolina is set for 1 p.m. (ET) or Noon (CT).
